<zyQHint> dogCount is 5. 5 <!-- - -->+ 3 is calculated, and animalsTotal is assigned with the result.</zyQHint>
<zyQExpl> The statement reads the value of dogCount (5), <!--subtracts-->adds 3, and assigns animalsTotal with the result of <!--2-->8.</zyQExpl>
</zyQ>

<zyQ>
<zyQText> dogCount is 5. What is in dogCount after executing the statement below?<br /><br />
<zyCode language="cpp" nobox="true">animalsTotal = dogCount <!-- - -->+ 3;</zyCode>
</zyQText>
<zyQAns>5</zyQAns>
